jasperReport.name: surveil
jasperReport.queryString:
select distinct t_surveil_id ,b_icd10.icd10_description as dx ,t_surveil.surveil_icd10_number ||'('||group_icd10_group_rp506||')' as icd10 --,group_icd10_group_rp506 as group ,f_patient_prefix.patient_prefix_description ||' '||t_patient.patient_firstname ||' ' ||t_patient.patient_lastname as patient_name ,to_date(((to_number(substring(t_patient.patient_birthday, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_patient.patient_birthday, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as patient_birthday ,CASE WHEN (t_patient.f_sex_id = '1') THEN 'ชาย' WHEN (t_patient.f_sex_id = '2') THEN 'หญิง' WHEN ((t_patient.f_sex_id <> '1') and (t_patient.f_sex_id <> '2')) THEN 'ไม่ระบุ' END as patient_sex ,CASE WHEN t_health_family.patient_birthday <> '' then to_number(substring(' ' ||age(to_date(((to_number(substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD'), to_date(((to_number(substring(t_health_family.patient_birthday, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_health_family.patient_birthday, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) from '(...)year'), '999') end as age_year ,CASE WHEN t_health_family.patient_birthday <> '' then to_number(substring(' ' ||age(to_date(((to_number(substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD'), to_date(((to_number(substring(t_health_family.patient_birthday, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_health_family.patient_birthday, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) from '(...)mons'), '999') end as age_month ,CASE WHEN t_health_family.patient_birthday <> '' then to_number(substring(' ' ||age(to_date(((to_number(substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD'), to_date(((to_number(substring(t_health_family.patient_birthday, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_health_family.patient_birthday, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) from '(...)days'), '999') end as age_day ,case when t_patient.patient_father_firstname = '' then t_patient.patient_mother_firstname else t_patient.patient_father_firstname end as parent_name ,t_patient.patient_hn as patient_hn ,f_patient_marriage_status.patient_marriage_status_description as patient_status ,f_patient_nation.patient_nation_description as patient_race ,f_patient_religion.patient_religion_description as patient_nation ,f_patient_occupation.patient_occupation_description as patient_occupation ,t_patient.patient_house as address,t_patient.patient_moo as moo ,tambol.address_description as tb ,amphur.address_description as amphur ,f_address.address_description as changwat ,t_patient.patient_contact_house as contact_address , t_patient.patient_contact_moo as contact_moo ,tambol_1.address_description as contact_tb ,amphur_1.address_description as contact_amphur ,changwat_1.address_description as contact_changwat ,case when t_health_village.b_health_village_location_id = '7130000000001' then 'เขตอบต.' when t_health_village.b_health_village_location_id = '7130000000002' then 'เขตเทศบาล' when t_health_village.b_health_village_location_id = '7130000000003' then 'ทั้งสองเขต.' when t_health_village.b_health_village_location_id = '7135547057349' then 'สภาตำบล.' else 'เขตอบต.(ชนบท)' end as patient_district ,SUBSTRING(t_surveil.surveil_sick_date,9,2) as sick_date ,to_date(((to_number(substring(t_surveil.surveil_sick_date, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_surveil.surveil_sick_date, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS sick_month ,SUBSTRING(t_surveil.surveil_sick_date,1,4) AS sick_year ,substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time,9,2) as visit_date ,to_date(((to_number(substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as visit_month ,substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time,1,4) as visit_year ,f_chronic_discharge_status.chronic_discharge_status_description as patient_description ,site_full_name as office_name , site_house as office_no ,site_moo as office_moo , f1.address_description as office_tb , f2.address_description as office_district , f3.address_description as office_province ,current_date as print_date
,substring(t_death.death_date_time,9,2) as death_date ,to_date(((to_number(substring(t_death.death_date_time, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_death.death_date_time, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as death_month ,substring(t_death.death_date_time,1,4) as death_year ,case when death_site = '2' then 'ตายในสถานพยาบาล' when death_site = '1' then 'ตายในสถานพยาบาล' else '' end as death_site ,to_date(((to_number(substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 1, 4), '9999') -543) || substring(t_visit.visit_begin_visit_time, 5, 6)), 'YYYY-MM-DD') as record_date FROM t_surveil LEFT JOIN t_visit ON (t_visit.t_patient_id = t_surveil.t_patient_id AND t_visit.f_visit_status_id <> '4' ) LEFT JOIN t_patient ON t_visit.t_patient_id = t_patient.t_patient_id LEFT JOIN f_patient_prefix ON t_patient.f_patient_prefix_id = f_patient_prefix.f_patient_prefix_id LEFT JOIN f_sex ON t_patient.f_sex_id = f_sex.f_sex_id LEFT JOIN f_address as tambol ON t_patient.patient_tambon = tambol.f_address_id LEFT JOIN f_address as amphur ON t_patient.patient_amphur = amphur.f_address_id LEFT JOIN f_address ON t_patient.patient_changwat = f_address.f_address_id LEFT JOIN f_address as tambol_1 ON t_patient.patient_contact_tambon = tambol_1.f_address_id LEFT JOIN f_address as amphur_1 ON t_patient.patient_contact_amphur = amphur_1.f_address_id LEFT JOIN f_address as changwat_1 ON t_patient.patient_contact_changwat = changwat_1.f_address_id LEFT JOIN f_patient_occupation ON t_patient.f_patient_occupation_id = f_patient_occupation.f_patient_occupation_id LEFT JOIN f_patient_nation ON t_patient.f_patient_nation_id = f_patient_nation.f_patient_nation_id LEFT JOIN f_patient_marriage_status ON t_patient.f_patient_marriage_status_id = f_patient_marriage_status.f_patient_marriage_status_id LEFT JOIN f_visit_type ON t_visit.f_visit_type_id = f_visit_type.f_visit_type_id LEFT JOIN f_patient_religion ON f_patient_religion.f_patient_religion_id = t_patient.f_patient_religion_id LEFT JOIN t_health_family ON t_health_family.t_health_family_id = t_patient.t_health_family_id LEFT JOIN t_health_home ON t_health_family.t_health_home_id = t_health_home.t_health_home_id LEFT JOIN t_health_village ON t_health_village.t_health_village_id = t_health_home.t_health_village_id
LEFT JOIN t_diag_icd10 ON (t_diag_icd10.diag_icd10_vn = t_visit.t_visit_id AND t_diag_icd10.diag_icd10_number = surveil_icd10_number AND t_diag_icd10.diag_icd10_active ='1') LEFT JOIN b_employee ON b_employee.b_employee_id = t_diag_icd10.diag_icd10_staff_doctor INNER JOIN b_icd10 ON surveil_icd10_number = b_icd10.icd10_number INNER JOIN b_group_icd10 on substring(surveil_icd10_number,1,3) = b_group_icd10.group_icd10_number LEFT JOIN f_chronic_discharge_status ON t_surveil.f_chronic_discharge_status_id = f_chronic_discharge_status.f_chronic_discharge_status_id LEFT JOIN t_death on (t_patient.t_patient_id = t_death.t_patient_id and death_active = '1') ,b_site inner join f_address f1 on b_site.site_tambon = f1.f_address_id inner join f_address f2 on b_site.site_amphur = f2.f_address_id inner join f_address f3 on b_site.site_changwat = f3.f_address_id
WHERE b_group_icd10.group_icd10_group_rp506 <> '99' AND b_group_icd10.group_icd10_group_rp506 <> '' AND t_surveil_id = $P{surveil_id}
